Class BinaryMipMapStrategy

java.lang.Object
  org.timepedia.chronoscope.client.data.BinaryMipMapStrategy
All Implemented Interfaces:
MipMapStrategy
public abstract class BinaryMipMapStrategy
extends java.lang.Object
implements MipMapStrategy

Mipmap strategy that uses a simple binary partitioning algorithm; essentially, each pair of datapoints at level n are aggregated into a single datapoint at level n+1.

Author:
Chad Takahashi
